      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "- Refactored the conversion pipeline into a dedicated service for cleaner flow and easier future extensions.\r\n- Improved frontmatter parsing and output handling to better cover edge cases and produce consistent results.\r\n- Resolve newline placeholders at load time and decode escape sequences from settings so conversions respect intended formatting.\r\n- Documented escape placeholders in settings and refreshed README content to match current behavior.\r\n- Added section output/extraction coverage and broadened test cases to lock in expected behavior.",
