      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "✨️Command Behavior Change: `Fold all indentation level 1-5`\r\n\r\nWe have updated the internal behavior of the `Fold all indentation level 1-5` command to improve its efficiency.\r\n\r\nPreviously: To fold multiple lines, plugin had to move the cursor to each line and execute the fold command repeatedly.\r\nNow: With this update, plugin can use multiple cursors to select all the lines you want to fold and then fold them all at once in a single operation.\r\n\r\nThis enhancement is expected to significantly speed up your workflow.",
